{"tid":2212591,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"成人片公司SOD主理：大人的主題樂園「SOD LAND」即將開幕","createTime":"2020-09-22T02:46:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-24T14:34:24.000Z","uid":137088,"like":356,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":107,"replies":[{"pid":"d0110b6e3e4b89755338edbca877ebcc4919ecd2","tid":2212591,"uid":137088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T02:46:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.likejapan.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/%E6%88%90%E4%BA%BA%E7%89%87%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8SOD%E4%B8%BB%E7%90%86%EF%BC%9A%E5%A4%A7%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%BB%E9%A1%8C%E6%A8%82%E5%9C%92%E3%80%8CSOD-LAND%E3%80%8D%E5%8D%B3%E5%B0%87%E9%96%8B%E5%B9%95-1024x576.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.likejapan.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2F%25E6%2588%2590%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%2589%2587%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258F%25B8SOD%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E7%2590%2586%25EF%25BC%259A%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%259A%2584%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E9%25A1%258C%25E6%25A8%2582%25E5%259C%2592%25E3%2580%258CSOD-LAND%25E3%2580%258D%25E5%258D%25B3%25E5%25B0%2587%25E9%2596%258B%25E5%25B9%2595-1024x576.jpg&h=67107fd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本最大的成人影片公司之一的SOD（Soft On Demand ソフト・オン・デマンド）近日宣布大人們的主題樂園「SOD LAND」將於2020年10月10日開幕。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.likejapan.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/SOD%E9%85%92%E5%A0%B41.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.likejapan.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2FSOD%25E9%2585%2592%25E5%25A0%25B41.jpg&h=4953afad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n將於新宿歌舞町開業的「SOD LAND」由共有5層（B1F-4F）不同概念的店舖組成。不同日媒消息介紹了SOD LAND每層主題：<br />\n<br />\nB1/F：SOD女子社員酒場 ウブ新入社員店（新人層）<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.likejapan.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/sod2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.likejapan.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2Fsod2.jpg&h=e2e6fb97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1/F：SOD LAND 総合受付（女子社員層）<br />\n<br />\n2/F：風俗研究所 「カクブツサロン」（風俗研究所層）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.likejapan.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/sod3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.likejapan.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2Fsod3.jpg&h=2e4cfb09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3/F：SOD Syain Bar KABUKICHO（有名AV女優層）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.likejapan.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/sod4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.likejapan.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2Fsod4.jpg&h=2489f210&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4/F：SILENT BAR（AV女優層）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.likejapan.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/sod5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.likejapan.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2Fsod5.jpg&h=e823f28e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.likejapan.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/SOD%E9%85%92%E5%A0%B42.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.likejapan.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2FSOD%25E9%2585%2592%25E5%25A0%25B42.jpg&h=c7dca84e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSOD LAND<br />\n<br />\n地址：東京都新宿區歌舞伎町1-21-3 フルフルビル<br />\n前往方法：西武新宿線西武新宿站徒歩1分鐘、JR山手線新宿站徒歩5分鐘<br />\n營業時間：17:00～22:00（實際營業時間或有改動）<br />\n<br />\n為對應肺炎疫情，官方指已引入最新的設備和實施最高水平的防疫措施，包括：<br />\n<br />\n1. Sense Thunder：<br />\n以AI識別樣貌及準確篩查發燒情況。戴著口罩可以測量溫度。<br />\n<br />\n2. Three of Defense<br />\n踩在墊板上時，會使用對人體無害的無酒精消毒噴霧進行全身消毒。<br />\n<br />\n3. エアロシールド（Aero Shield）<br />\n室內設有殺菌力強的UV-C紫外線照射裝置，保持安全、安心的環境。<br />\n<br />\n4. LAFUADO FILTER<br />\n冷氣已安裝具有防病毒功能的高性能空調過濾器，立即轉淨化空氣，對室內滅菌和除臭也有效。"},{"pid":"cbd3ab07e8a1e8b5af8a7ea007ca04b2e4ecd4aa","tid":2212591,"uid":68689,"like":347,"dislike":4,"score":343,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T02:48:07.000Z","msg":"見到咁多防疫措施<br />\n究竟到時D肺炎毒D定D客個樣毒D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"531cecb6ee9013b6f44bc07bed89ef26d6091617","tid":2212591,"uid":137088,"like":160,"dislike":6,"scor